data.text:
On Wednesday, President @JunckerEU will travel to Washington where he will be received by President @realDonaldTrump at the White House.

60 years of EU visits to the @WhiteHouse in pictures ↓ https://t.co/MH8CSUa5fu

Which issues matter to you?
Share and discuss your ideas for a European citizens' initiative in the forum → https://t.co/OmOfY2trS2
#EUTakeTheInitiative #ECI https://t.co/xAzGfhCpwz

Apply for the European Sustainability Award! 
We are championing inspiring initiatives that turn the global Sustainable Development Goals into concrete results.
Find out how to enter the competition here: https://t.co/P3zL0eNe4c #EUSustainabilityAward #SDGs https://t.co/NGKifWr8Oq

Registration for paid traineeships in the European Commission is now open!
Apply for the March 2019 session by the end of August → https://t.co/EH3wA7xYFE https://t.co/ccvij0LEVA

The provincial hospital in Toruń, Poland, is being expanded and modernised with the backing of the European Fund for Strategic Investments https://t.co/gH6KDFM4fY #investEU #EFSI https://t.co/n1cmZg5sx2

Are you #ReadyToChange your relationship with plastics?
Don't be drawn in by the flamboyant plastic straw - one of the top 10 most commonly found items on EU beaches.
Help protect our oceans → https://t.co/YQfCUFvef3 #PlasticsStrategy https://t.co/CF3PweXY6q

The Investment Plan for Europe has reached its original objective of mobilising €315 billion in investments, of which 2/3 are private. Our next goal is to raise that figure to €500 billion by 2020 #investEU https://t.co/vlvY7J11KP

We are home to more than 140 km of documents detailing our shared European history – this represents the distance between Brussels and the Hague!
You can now access our #EUarchives in different languages online or visit us in Brussels → https://t.co/NmvLEwQr8b #Archive30 https://t.co/z82cZ02dox

It all starts tomorrow! 
We will embark on a journey throughout time with our participation to the #Archive30 challenge.
Stay tuned, we found some amazing gems from our #EUarchives… https://t.co/AtetAgIC3H
